description:
Reports deprecated classes, methods, and fields that are used in your code nonetheless. Example: 'class MyCode {
    @Deprecated
    void oldMethod() {}// warning: "Deprecated member is still used"

    void newMethod() {
      oldMethod(); // forgotten usage
    }
  }' Usages within deprecated elements are ignored. NOTE: Due to performance reasons, a non-private member is checked only when its name rarely occurs in the project. Inspection ID: DeprecatedIsStillUsed
